<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Welcome to Badlaav — your account is ready</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background: #FFF0EA; color: #373735; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px; }
    .header { border-bottom: 2px solid #FAD062; padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .brand { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #015243; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .tagline { font-size: 11px; color: #7a756f; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 4px; }
    h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; color: #015243; margin: 0 0 16px; line-height: 1.2; }
    p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #373735; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .cta-box { background: #015243; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .cta-box p { color: #e8f4f8; margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 14px; }
    .cta-link { display: inline-block; background: #FAD062; color: #0d1b2a; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 3px; text-decoration: none; }
    .footer { margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #e6d4c8; font-size: 11px; color: #7a756f; }
    a { color: #3d7a8a; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="brand">Badlaav</div>
      <div class="tagline">A turning point, not a trip.</div>
    </div>

    <h1>Your account is ready.</h1>

    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>We've created an account for you from your registration. No password needed — sign in with your email and a 6-digit code we'll send you.</p>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <p>Go to the sign-in page and enter this email address. We'll send a 6-digit code.</p>
      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="cta-link">Sign In</a>
    </div>

    <p>From your account you can view your registration, download your invoice, and track upcoming batch details.</p>

    <p>— Arjun, Badlaav</p>

    <div class="footer">
      Badlaav · Ambajogai, Maharashtra<br />
      <a href="mailto:iambadlaav@gmail.com">iambadlaav@gmail.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
